quran[9{c,v,t}:
30,16,aur jinhon ne kufar kya hai aur hamari ayaat ko aur akhirat ki mulaqaat ko jhatlaya hai woh azaab mein haazir rakhay jayen ge
30,17,pas tasbeeh karo Allah ki jabkay tum shaam karte ho aur jab subah karte ho
30,18,asmano aur zameen mein usi ke liye hamd hai aur ( tasbeeh karo is ki ) teesray pehar aur jabkay tum par Zahar ka waqt aata hai
30,19,woh zindah mein se murdy ko nikalta hai aur murdy mein se zindah ko nikalta hai aur zameen ko is ki mout ke baad zindagi bakhshta hai isi terhan tum log bhi ( haalat mout se ) nikaal liye jao ge
30,20,uss ki nishanion mein se yeh hai ke is ne tum ko matti se peda kya phir yakayak tum bashar ho ke ( zameen mein ) phailtay chalay ja rahay ho
30,21,aur is ki nishanion mein se yeh hai ke is ne tumahray liye tumhari hi jins se biwiyan banayen taakay tum un ke paas sukoon haasil karo aur tumahray darmain mohabbat aur rehmat peda kar di yaqeenan is mein bohat si nishanain hai unn logon ke liye jo ghhor o fikar karte hain
30,22,"aur is ki nishanion mein se asmano aur zameen ki paidaiesh, aur tumhari zabanon aur tumahray rangon ka ikhtilaaf hai yaqeenan is mein bohat si nishanain hain danishmand logon ke liye"
30,23,aur uss ki nishanion mein se tumhara raat aur din ko sona aur tumhara is ke fazl ko talaash karna hai yaqeenan iss mein bohat si nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo ( ghhor se ) suntay hain
30,24,"aur uss ki nishanion mein se yeh hai ke woh tumhe bijli ki chamak dekhata hai khauf ke sath bhi aur tama ke sath bhi aur aasman se pani barsata hai, phir is ke zareya se zameen ko is ki mout ke baad zindagi bakhshta hai yaqeenan iss mein bohat si nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo aqal se kaam letay hain"
